si_remarks: Humberto Rocha and Helber Freitas and Helber Freitas and Helber Freitas provided precipitation and radiation data ( Laboratório de Clima e Biosfera do IAG-USP). The other responsible for the sap flow and environmental data (experimental desing and collection of data) that must be also listed as coauthors  are Rafael S. Oliveira (Unicamp), Marcos P. M.
